## 3. 디자인 시스템

### 3.1 CSS Variables (style.css)

```css
:root {
  /* Colors */
  --color-primary: #2e7d32;
  --color-primary-light: #4caf50;
  --color-primary-dark: #1b5e20;

  --color-success: #4caf50;
  --color-warning: #ff9800;
  --color-error: #f44336;
  --color-info: #2196f3;

  --color-bg: #f5f7fa;
  --color-surface: #ffffff;
